h3cFtmManMIB.name: h3cFtmManMIB
h3cFtmManMIB.description: this mib will maintain Fabric topology management. The mib includes unit-id, unit-name and fabric authentication information.

h3cFtmUnitTable.name: h3cFtmUnitTable
h3cFtmUnitTable.description: A table of informations of XRN-Fabric Unit.

h3cFtmUnitEntry.name: h3cFtmUnitEntry
h3cFtmUnitEntry.description: An entry for configuring unit informations of XRN-Fabric.

h3cFtmIndex.name: h3cFtmIndex
h3cFtmIndex.description: The unique index of a unit.

h3cFtmUnitID.name: h3cFtmUnitID
h3cFtmUnitID.description: Identifer of unit in fabric. Its value should be between 1 and the maximum which defines in product specification. An exception is described in description of h3cFtmNumberMode. In that case, the value of this object remains its original value after set to zero.

h3cFtmUnitName.name: h3cFtmUnitName
h3cFtmUnitName.description: Name of unit in XRN-Fabric. It consists of no more than 64 characters.

h3cFtmUnitRole.name: h3cFtmUnitRole
h3cFtmUnitRole.description: Role of unit in XRN-Fabric. One unit in a XRN-Fabric acts as master role and others act as slave roles

h3cFtmNumberMode.name: h3cFtmNumberMode
h3cFtmNumberMode.description: Numbering Mode of unit in XRN-Fabric. If the unit ID is assigned by the auto numbering algorithm, the numbering mode will be automatic numbering; if the unit ID (h3cFtmUnitID) is assigned by the user, the numbering mode will be manual numbering; if h3cFtmUnitID is set to be zero, the numbering mode will become automatic numbering.

h3cFtmAuthValue.name: h3cFtmAuthValue
h3cFtmAuthValue.description: Authentication value of XRN-Fabric Feature. ftm_none mode means no authentication. In simple mode, the value is password of a string of 1 to 16 charactors. While in md5 mode, the value is key of a string within 16 charactors.

h3cFtmFabricVlanID.name: h3cFtmFabricVlanID
h3cFtmFabricVlanID.description: The object is used for get and set the Fabric VlanID. Only is the equipment not in the stacking status, the value can be set.

h3cFtmFabricType.name: h3cFtmFabricType
h3cFtmFabricType.description: Topology type of Fabric. outofStack means this unit is not in stack.

h3cFtmUnitIDChange.name: h3cFtmUnitIDChange
h3cFtmUnitIDChange.description: When unit id changes in fabric, this trap is sent with unit index and its new id .

h3cFtmUnitNameChange.name: h3cFtmUnitNameChange
h3cFtmUnitNameChange.description: When unit name changes in fabric, this trap is sent with unit index and its new name.

h3cFtmMIBCompliance.name: h3cFtmMIBCompliance
h3cFtmMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for FTM implementing the MIB.

h3cFtmConfigGroup.name: h3cFtmConfigGroup
h3cFtmConfigGroup.description: The basic collection of objects for sending trap of FTM Management.

h3cFtmNotificationGroup.name: h3cFtmNotificationGroup
h3cFtmNotificationGroup.description: The basic collection of objects for sending trap of FTM Management.
